      "span_text": "The recently proposed methods such as Xception (Chollet 2016) and ResNext [CITATION_1] ) use special depth-wise convolution operation to reduce its total number of parameters and to improve performance, in our work, we do not use this new convolution operation, so it can't be compared fairly, and we will consider this in our future work to further improve the performance."
